      <title>移民冲突后德国总理默茨将重点关注经济政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/germany-s-merz-to-focus-on-economic-policy-after-migration-clash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周，在围绕更严格的移民规则展开的激烈争论之后，德国大选中保守党领跑者弗里德里希·梅尔茨将把竞选重点放在振兴陷入困境的经济的提案上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/germany-s-merz-to-focus-on-economic-policy-after-migration-clash</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
