    <item>
      <title>法国总理面临预算纠纷的危险：值得关注的事项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/france-s-premier-risks-turmoil-in-budget-showdown-what-to-watch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理弗朗索瓦·贝鲁周一面临一场生死攸关的考验，他计划在不经过议会投票的情况下批准新预算，这一危险的过程可能会导致法国在不到一年的时间内第三届政府垮台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/france-s-premier-risks-turmoil-in-budget-showdown-what-to-watch</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普提高欧盟关税威胁，计划与加拿大和墨西哥通话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-says-tariffs-will-definitely-happen-with-european-union</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普加大了对欧盟的关税威胁，同时表示他将与加拿大和墨西哥领导人进行会谈。在贸易战前景变成现实的忙碌周末过后，股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-says-tariffs-will-definitely-happen-with-european-union</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 00:41:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
