    <item>
      <title>特朗普对中国征收 10% 关税后，习近平考虑采取报复措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/xi-weighs-retaliation-after-trump-hits-china-with-10-tariff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普发动新一轮贸易战后，加拿大和墨西哥领导人迅速作出回应，而中国国家主席习近平则在宣布具体反击措施之前稍事休息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/xi-weighs-retaliation-after-trump-hits-china-with-10-tariff</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 13:40:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度回应特朗普 力图摆脱“关税之王”称号</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/shun-protectionism-india-signals-to-industry-with-tariff-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度政府在预算中大幅削减了进口关税，并表示不会利用保护主义措施来庇护企业，这显然是为了阻止美国总统唐纳德·特朗普与其主要合作伙伴发动新一轮贸易战的报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/shun-protectionism-india-signals-to-industry-with-tariff-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 12:16:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
